@KanbanApi_HostAddress = http://localhost:5200

### Get Boards for User "user1"
GET {{KanbanApi_HostAddress}}/boards?userId=user1
Accept: application/json

### Create a New Board
POST {{KanbanApi_HostAddress}}/boards
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Project Alpha",
  "description": "Main project board",
  "userId": "user1"
}

### Get Board by ID (Assuming ID 1 was created)
GET {{KanbanApi_HostAddress}}/boards/1
Accept: application/json

### Update Board
PUT {{KanbanApi_HostAddress}}/boards/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 1,
  "name": "Project Alpha V2",
  "description": "Updated description",
  "userId": "user1"
}

### Delete Board
DELETE {{KanbanApi_HostAddress}}/boards/1
Accept: application/json
